h3. Workaround
Post pages in a strict sequential manner

According to this documentation:
 {quote}
Whenever you add a link to Jira issues in Confluence, or link to a Confluence page from your Jira application, the *Jira Links* button appears at the top of the Confluence page. This means you can quickly jump from Confluence to Jira and vice versa, speeding up your workflow.{quote}

It would be convenient if we could provide our customer to disable restricted page from been display on the Jira tickets.

